               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Mar Yǝsḥaq, Book of Mar Isaac of Nineveh (fols. 3ra-149rb)
 
                     Additio 1.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">


                     <note>The text contains 34 "paragraphs" (አንቀጽ) with numbers indicated by
                        numerals (e.g., ፳, ፴ወ፪) or written out (ቀዳማዊ, ራብዕ); but other wise
                        discourses (ነገር) (<locus target="#46ra">46ra</locus>, 54rb, 56vb), chapters
                        (ምዕራፍ) (<locus target="#69rb">69rb</locus>, 101rb, 107va), prayers (ጸሎት)
                           (<locus target="#87va">87va</locus>, 92rb, 111vb) and the concluding
                        homily (<locus target="#145ra">145ra</locus>).</note>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
